cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR

The paper deals with the development of algorithms for scene recognition and object detection in challenging environments, which are important topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The use of deep fusion models and machine learning techniques also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the evaluation of the algorithms on image datasets and real-world videos suggests a possible connection to information retrieval (cs.IR).
